Package edu.cnm.deepdive.ironorimgtransform.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GaussianBlur
    This class extends the TransformOperation class.
    GoogleSignInService  
    TransformDBService
    Provides a service layer for accessing the TransformDB Room/SQLite database.
    TransformDBService.DeleteTransformTask
    Implements an asynchronous DELETE of one or more Image instances from the local database.
    TransformDBService.GetHistoryTask
    Implements an asynchronous INSERT of one or more Image instances into the local database.
    TransformDBService.InsertApodTask
    Implements an asynchronous INSERT of one or more Transform instances, with related Image instances, into the local database.
    TransformDBService.SelectAllTrasformTask
    Implements an asynchronous SELECT of all Transform instances (sorted in descending date order) from the local database.
    TransformDBService.SelectApodTask
    Implements an asynchronous SELECT of a single Transform instance, and an INSERT of a related Image instance, in the local database.
    TransformOperation
    Classes of Transform entities extend this class so that individual transform types are forced to inherit and thus implement the TransformOperation.transform(Bitmap, View) method and the TransformOperation.getLayout() method.
    Utility
    This service class requests permission to access external storage permission at runtime.
